dc:description: Pinkish buff micaceous clay.  Modern hanging lamp.  Nozzle has blunt end and concave sides.  Incised ovule pattern on rim.  Ring handle with two grooves rises from center of lamp.  Filling hole at right of handle.  Plain reverse.  Bronze chain (about 13.5 cm) attached to handle ends in large ring.
